img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下兩邊<br />\n條女有澄清話佢地個關係好似老母教仔，話俾左一個月事主改但沒效咁話喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話佢其實唔鍾意打機，睇事主打機都係因為愛過事主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以想用彩蛋修保關係係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有話同事主細佬沒野，因為分左手之後事主派佢細佬睇實條女，所以先俾人覺得佢地好close<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}